  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to anjuta</title>

    <para><application>Anjuta DevStudio</application> is a versatile software development
    studio featuring a number of advanced programming facilities including project
    management, application wizard, interactive debugger, source editor, version control,
    GUI designer, profiler.</para>

    &lfs70_built;

